page.title: 40A day in the life.
page.content:
Saturday 18th June 2011

I played on the trampoline then I had lunch. Then I went to my friend’s house for a party. The reason why we went there was because his brother was turning three.

I played on the trampoline and then prank called a random person then I prank called my friend’s mum. I played with Lochan and Gabe, we played hide and seek.


pupil-Montbelle School
